## Failure Modes to Watch

| Failure Mode                          | Risk | Mitigation |
|---------------------------------------|------|------------|
| HStack with fixed-width children      | HIGH | Cap with prefix + +N badge; verify math |
| Card VStack without maxWidth frame    | HIGH | Always add `.frame(maxWidth: .infinity)` first |
| `.fixedSize(horizontal: true)`        | HIGH | Banned — remove immediately |
| LazyHStack without bounded parent     | HIGH | Wrap in explicit width container |
| Text with `.lineLimit(1)` and no truncation | MED | Add `.truncationMode(.tail)` |
| GeometryReader returning proxy.size.width fed back to frame | MED | Read-only; never set frame from geometry width + offset |
| New card added without `.frame(maxWidth: .infinity)` | MED | Add to card inventory above |
